field_accordian.field_content:
The choice of ACTs in a country or region should be based on optimal efficacy, safety and adherence.<br>
&nbsp;
<p class="statement" style="background-color:rgb( 102 , 204 , 255 );  padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 5px;"><span style="color:#0000cd"><em>Good practice statement</em></span></p></tbody>

Drugs used in IPTp, SMC and IPTi should not be used as a component of first- line treatments in the same country or region.<br>
&nbsp;
<p class="statement" style="background-color:rgb( 102 , 204 , 255 );  padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 5px;"><span style="color:#0000cd"><em>Good practice statement</em></span></p></tbody>
